{"tid":1262597,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知呢期TVB新聞部收到咩投訴最多？","createTime":"2019-06-27T18:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T19:09:47.000Z","uid":72534,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9350f0d605711286f2f63e60434a0b57cbd4df54","tid":1262597,"uid":72534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"發夢朋友報夢話<br />\n大約21至24號期間<br />\nTVB新聞部收到13份意見係話報導偏袒示威者：1份偏袒警察<br />\nIf投訴 佢係要向政府解釋 審稿條友一身蟻<br />\n<br />\n如果你相信向公務員事務局投訴警察<br />\n可以係令克警中招<br />\n咁點解唔試下寄封Email/打個電話試試<br />\n上網有齊方法<br />\n<br />\n1. 向TVB<br />\n郵寄地址 : 九龍將軍澳工業村駿才街77號電視廣播城<br />\n電話 : 2335 9123<br />\n傳真 : 2358 1300<br />\n電郵地址 : tvbpr@tvb.com.hk <br />\n<br />\n2.經通訊局<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/tc/content_508/ca_complaint_form_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_508%2Fca_complaint_form_c.pdf&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPKdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=53e6e98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/tc/content_508/ca_complaint_form_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n郵寄或傳真投訴至通訊事務管理局（下載投訴表格 ）；或<br />\n郵遞地址：香港灣仔皇后大道東213號胡忠大廈20樓通訊事務管理局<br />\n傳真號碼：(852) 2507 2219<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住搞清楚<br />\n係要克警受到應有嘅懲罰<br />\n係要佢上庭受審<br />\n<strong>唔係行私刑令自己變到同克警一撚樣</strong><br />\n<strong>DLLM 咪用電筒射攝影師眼</strong><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果你唔知電視台新聞部運作<br />\n區家麟有解說<br />\n<a href=\"http://hktext.blogspot.com/2014/10/humiliation.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhktext.blogspot.com%2F2014%2F10%2Fhumiliation.html%3Fm%3D1&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPKdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=5f55c613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hktext.blogspot.com/2014/10/humiliation.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>DLLM 咪再搞前線記者同攝影師<br />\n下次佢見到暗角七警2.0就直接移開鏡頭 </strong>"},{"pid":"c03d3dfe0484894aec4eba264c0a4fdaccedadb7","tid":1262597,"uid":912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:46:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n呢啲先係有用嘅post"},{"pid":"bdc00af1d9ee165221cea9177357e0cdd8fc8abe","tid":1262597,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:48:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9e607f26715f23a38212584f93bfc80afe104fb9","tid":1262597,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:49:38.000Z","msg":"幫push"},{"pid":"33e91b07c7f4a2b98e079e1a802dc53be640eed5","tid":1262597,"uid":31906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:49:57.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"6463d8903eecb90215e010e36cfe9d587e07c081","tid":1262597,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:51:04.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"4f6809fc586fa96f3ef45162eea6c9ff97c5d9aa","tid":1262597,"uid":266107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"屌 向tvb投訴<br />\n根本冇覆過我 有撚用"},{"pid":"3cc2b398744eb487b7a01addd8727d71a99ddc6c","tid":1262597,"uid":30290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:54:01.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得通訊局係有用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府對紅底媒體會有幾嚴重既處罸？<br />\n睇番舊時最多都係罸錢，我諗tvb 奶得共都唔志在啦。<br />\n真係要搞都一定係起底，或者叫其他人罷買好過"},{"pid":"1f516a8534e23abde1d170cd363edba8bc7ce584","tid":1262597,"uid":912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f6809fc586fa96f3ef45162eea6c9ff97c5d9aa","tid":1262597,"uid":266107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"屌 向tvb投訴<br />\n根本冇覆過我 有撚用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2